channel.title: How Much have you made/spent on SCAR?
channel.description:
I've Made About 12m In about a month. Not really autoing that much.
I've spent about 2.8m on scar scripts. (half i havn't even used)
What about you?

item.title: How Much have you made/spent on SCAR?
item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

We cud just make a auto eat script, and just let the script stand where a monster attacks...

Yeah, it’s been done. But the monsters stop attacking after 15 minutes, so you need to have a walkaway and walkback. Combine that with randoms etc… and making an autofighter is a good bit of work.

Sorta, but not really noticed it. I saw one of those chineese bot ppl sellin 900k lobs r0fl! He showed me them...

Yeah. The Chinese pretty much work legit, too. They just use multiple clients and work 10+ accounts at the same time. I’m sure some of them bot, but alot just legit a whole lot of accounts at once. They apparantly all work together in big companies where they earn pennies. But fuck it, free room and board and getting paid to play video games? Sick deal if you ask me, but I’d rather be a WoW farmer.
